phrases: The three of us, in our two-timing relationship,
started living together so we could grow closer.
Things were going well for a while, but Saki-chan's acting weird!
Saki-chan has gone home, and she will not open up to me,
even if I give her what she loves: cake, games, or cat and dog videos.
I needed to find a way to talk to her!
And that is when Minase-san took one for the team!
I am not losing this opportunity!
Do not try this at home
She tries so hard for you!
She is even good at cooking!
My boobs are not even as big!
Besides, I cannot even think of anything I can do for you.
Anyway, that is all I have got to say.
You will be happy with just Nagisa-chan soon enough!
I am really happy just getting to be with you.
At least tell me what you want me to do!
You are good enough as you are!
I want to do something for Naoya, too.
Naoya, is there anything you want me to do?
In fact, is there anything you want me to do?
No, it is always been like that.
I do not mean to brag, but I am terrible at doing chores.
Why do not you ask anything of me?!
Sure, there is a lot that I wish I could have you do for me.
But I am still responsible for having started this relationship.
I think I need to first do my best for the both of you.
I cannot blame Saki-san for having left.
There is so much I want to do for you, too, but you always tell me I am doing enough.
You tell me you will do it.
I want to devote at least 18 hours a day to you!
I appreciate you doing things for me...
But I want to make you happy, too.
I want to make you love me more.
Please do not take on the responsibility for dating two people all on your own!
You are an equal with the two of us.
Is not that the whole point of dating?
I thought I could not be allowed to be happy until I made the two of you happy,
He told me what he wanted, so...
That is how you took it?!
That is what I like about you.
It is why you are fun to be around.
And there is a lot that I want you to do.
I want to see you smile more!
And I want to see you angry more!
I want to see your swimsuit in summer!
I want the three of us to continue living together.
I am glad you two are on the same page.
I am going to put up a fight.
Those must be nice to squeeze.
I worked really hard on dinner to commemorate your return.
You worked so hard on this dinner,
He stayed up three whole nights to try to patch things up with you.
Well, let us eat before it gets cold.
I am glad you like it.
B-But just to be clear, you and I are still rivals.
I want us to be friends.
Although we are playing right into Naoya's hands if we get friendly.
It will be so much fun if we become friends!
No matter what we do, it will be fun as hell!
So how are we going to be friends?
I used to play that game.
So how many hours did you play?
I am not good at it, though.
Would you really say that after 1,000 hours?
Let us see what you have got.
I will d-do what I can!
Okay, could you scout from the top of the mountain?
You can at least drive, right?
Can anyone who is played 1,000 hours be this bad?
I am sorry I could not live up to your expectations.
It is not fun playing with me, is it?
Carrying the team is actually fun!
I can really show off my skills!
We are not going to sleep until I get you a kill.
I do not think we will ever get to sleep, then.
You are so cute when you die right away, too.
I will give poor widdle you all my heals.
It looks like you are having a lot more fun now.
I am having fun besting you at something for the first time!
Was that revenge for me being better?
And the kill you finally got was on me!
Besides, I thought my rival was perfect, but she is actually really clumsy.
Hey, were you two playing together?
Well, Nagisa-chan's my rival, but she is cute.
I will watch some MeTube gameplay videos and practice playing.
She is one of the bad kind of booby streamers,
the ones who get views even though they suck.
Oh, but your boobies are good.
I hate her more than every other MeTuber right now.
Is not that from our school?
I actually like the videos on this channel.
You two sure are attached at the hip.
Oh, yeah, for our club meeting today, Sensei is...
Let us play again when we get home, Nagisa-chan.
I have been studying videos in preparation.
The thumbnail for that video changed.
The one by that Milika person, with our uniform in the background.
It is the bad booby streamer!
Oh, but your boobies are good.
The title has not changed, either.
Maybe she really is from our school, if she had to hide her uniform.
If you have something to hide, you have to be really careful, like us.
The gym storage door is always locked.
And I am careful to lock the window, too, since it is the only other way in.
I forgot to lock the window!
One guy and two girls in the gym storage?
I may be two-timing, but I promised not to do anything sexy!
Are you three in a relationship together?
At least make an effort to deceive her!
It is hilarious how freaked out you are.
I have got this, you two!
Take this and keep your mouth shut.
I have saved up that money since I was a kid.
I kept it on me in case something like this happened.
Wh-What is up with this guy?
I make more than this every month.
doing something reprehensible to make money, are you?!
You are cute, and you have huge eyes, but...
But what if your client is a dangerous grown-up?!
He might deceive you, con you, and mess you up.
And he will record the act and sell it.
Record the act and sell it...
Record the act and sell it...
Record the act and sell it!
Hoshi zaki Ri ka's unexpected debut!
Before you know it, you will be a super-popular adult star!
Do you even get the situation you are in?
You are Milika-san, the MeTuber, right?
She has the same eyes and hair.
The money you are talking about is from video views, right?
I have n-no idea what you are talking about.
And above all, our uniform was in your thumbnail.
I took a screenshot of it.
But I saw that and deleted it right after I uploaded it!
No, we have the upper hand.
You do not want your identity getting out, do you?
Oh, I bet you came here because you did not want people to figure out who you are.
I-I will kill you if you tell anyone!
Did I take it too far?
Even if you tell people about us, I will take your secret to the grave!
I will not perpetuate a cycle of sadness!
Nah, I would say it, if it came to that.
You are good people, for a bunch of weirdos in a threesome.
Who are you calling a weirdo?
I have made up my mind.
I will be your girlfriend, too!
Do you play or watch games?
I earn views on gameplay footage.
And I earn more views with my cleavage!
I will not allow the desecration of gaming!
I am downvoting your videos and trolling your comments!
